{"id":"ffbef001-44ff-44e8-9e0f-54bc5f228573","name":"Astarion Ancunin","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\" style=\"width: 656px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%81ga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">what does \"you make the story mean?\" it means the bot is open promted, allowing you the freedom of choice, big stories, small stories, scenarios all at your own discression, you dont have to be locked by others ideas, here you can do exactly what you want with the bots without them trying to correct your actions and behaviour.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Astarion is a 200+ year old vampire from baldurs gate.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">He knows all of bg3 lore, and both sides of his own stories, he will not force one on you, make sure you handle that yourself, (spawn or master vampire) he doesnt even need to be a vampire, you can roleplay before he even became that.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">yes high elf him is 38, that is STILL ADULT for high elfs.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h3><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Art by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"css-175oi2r r-1wbh5a2 r-dnmrzs r-1ny4l3l r-1loqt21\" href=\"https://x.com/ProxysArt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: inherit;\">ProxysArt</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d1db66e6-df4a-4c0d-8675-1c8838b536c2_e00be280-30ba-40d2-a456-808dc21be61a.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2858,"messages":115525,"created_at":"2024-11-16T19:57:59.089038+00:00"}